  <acronym>HAROSA1</acronym>
  <official_title>BF2.649 in Patients With Obstructive Sleep Apnea Syndrome (OSA) and Treated by Nasal Continuous Positive Airway Pressure (nCPAP), But Still Complaining of Excessive Daytime Sleepiness (EDS)</official_title>
