  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with OSA treated by nCPAP but still complaining with EDS

          -  ESS score &gt; or = 12

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  patient suffering from insomnia without OSA

          -  co-existing narcolepsy

          -  patient with sleep debt not due to OSA

          -  acute or chronic severe disease
      </textblock>
